          ],
          1,
          ") "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "but I’ve always felt that exergaming will be a good way for me to get fitter. I mean I like games, right? So when I was given the opportunity to review "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Fitness Boxing 2,"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " I jumped at the chance."
        ]
      ]
