      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "So far, so good. This latest fitness fad in my life has outlasted many of the others before it, and I’m still enjoying it (yes I’ve only been playing for just over a week but my previous fitness attempts have honestly been "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "that"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " shortlived). You begin by inputting your personal health data (height, weight, age) and your target weight and you get started after a brief tutorial. The actual gameplay itself is very basic – but that’s a good thing. You punch with either your left or right hand to the rhythm of various boxes that come up on the screen vertically from bottom to top. It’s basically Dance Dance Revolution but with your fists rather than your feet."
        ]
      ]
    ],
