          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Fitness Boxing"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " was released in 2018 and was a successful, if not ground-breaking, hit. The sequel builds on all the good work of the original and expands the gamification of the genre. By that, I mean there’s quite a few elements here that will intrigue and draw in a gamer such as myself; for example, there’s an unlockable in-game currency that can be used to unlock various extras, such as new music tracks and outfits for your trainers."
        ]
      ]
